      • isValidPageSetToken

        public boolean isValidPageSetToken(SCUIContext uiContext,
                                   java.lang.String pageSetToken)
        Determine whether the given token is valid and associated to the current session.

        A rule of thumb is to never use a PageSetToken unless it was returned by an API request via the current session. uiContext pageSetToken true if the token is in the session, false otherwise.
